{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"423522-all-jumbled-up","title":"¡Todo revuelto!","description":"Ammu está lista para salir al escenario pero no puede recordar sus líneas. Mucha diversión a la par que va mezclando sus líneas.","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Némesis Zerga"],"illustrators":["Sheena Deviah"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"CuenTale Cuentoteca digital","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/423522-all-jumbled-up"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727060/size3/c9b0c085cabd2aea8920ddfc909b90f4.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727060/size6/c9b0c085cabd2aea8920ddfc909b90f4.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99602/size6/f951651b59675b6d9c30d4015d2858f5.jpg","text":"Ammu está practicando sus líneas.\n—¿Sabes todas tus líneas? —preguntó la profesora Malati a Ammu.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/98241/size6/7ba85875e4a1caa1a83e215acc9bddd6.jpg","text":"“Radha vu... vu... vuela lejos,\nParakeet llora ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! El Rey se ha en... en... enfriado, querida mesa, el desayuno está listo”.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99606/size6/69f87ba7107f456987bf09c04e2eb5a9.jpg","text":"¡Oh no! Eso no está muy bien.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99607/size6/6708f972b967c9410dd700dc606791c0.jpg","text":"“El rey vu... vu... vuela lejos,\nla mesa llora ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! Radha se ha en... en... enfriado,\nquerido Parakeet, el desayuno está listo”.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99610/size6/e6694f4bd42e27253c14096a99a39fb4.jpg","text":"¡Oh no! Eso tampoco está bien.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99612/size6/9faf8e28c78d6458d4466b2f49e09351.jpg","text":"“La mesa vue... vu... vuela lejos,\nel rey llora ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! Parakeet se ha en... en... enfriado, querida Radha, el desayuno está listo”.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99613/size6/953e9d2f973c436b71b34e414ad86bc5.jpg","text":"¡Oh no! Algo sigue sin estar bien.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99614/size6/2e5fd2934b40907a903f4ffbd4d3b930.jpg","text":"—Ammu, es tu turno —llama la profe Malati.\nAmmu sube al escenario y dice:","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99615/size6/0ecb28d3a7eebb6fd6626b6524f03294.jpg","text":"“Parakeet vu... vu... vuela lejos, Radha llora ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! ¡Buaaaa! La comida en la mesa se ha en.. en.. enfriado, querido Rey, el desayuno está listo”.\n¡El público empieza a aplaudir!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99617/size6/b3786900864de93591364bd3e361808f.jpg","text":"11/11","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":10,"words":152}}